 \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hailey_Van_Lith\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hailey Van Lith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hailey_Van_Lith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hailey_Van_Lith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reuters  PARIS, France - Reigning champions the United States finally got a win on the board in their fourth game of the women's 3\\u00d73 basketball pool stage at the Paris Olympics on Thursday, August 1, with a 17-11 victory over Spain.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.999999943310742, \"rank\": 5.6678098548249e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9981356933998965, \"rank\": 0.0018677487255695073, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9905850954653697, \"rank\": 0.009498424635476338, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999374267665, \"rank\": 6.103785666174773e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After suffering a third consecutive defeat in a 17-15 loss to Australia earlier in the day, the US used their size advantage to make scoring drives and impose tight defense on Spain.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999426568155, \"rank\": 5.73291209766066e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999374267665, \"rank\": 6.103785666174773e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a great game for our team.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All it takes is one win sometimes to get going,\\\" said Hailey Van Lith.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hailey_Van_Lith\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hailey Van Lith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hailey_Van_Lith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hailey_Van_Lith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So hopefully that was the igniter to our fire.\\\"\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three-time Olympian Kevin Durant was at the Australia game, while four-time NBA champion LeBron James and swimmer Katie Ledecky, owner of 13 Olympic medals, were courtside to support their compatriots for the Spain game.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999194859735672, \"rank\": 8.052050933755684e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0588728492668163e-14, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.152592962036352e-16, \"text\": \"NBA champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\"}, {\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedi