mer_Fredette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmer_Fredette\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both US teams remain rooted to the bottom of the pool standings with their prospects of qualifying directly for the semi-finals looking bleak.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999426568155, \"rank\": 5.73291209766066e-08, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the pool stage, the teams play a round robin.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two from the pool go straight to the semi-finals and the next four teams play off for the other two spots in the last four.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Latvia had earlier pulled off a swift 22-8 victory over China to top the men's pool.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"score\": 0.9980269901537697, \"rank\": 0.001401681403593251, \"text\": \"Latvia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\"}, {\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984384661228456, \"rank\": 0.0015639193284621056, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Top-ranked Serbia beat the Netherlands 21-19 when Strahinja Stojacic ended the contest with an extraordinary long-range two-pointer.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999986777033529, \"rank\": 1.3221875401586551e-06, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999778795362399, \"rank\": 0.00021541422160395947, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strahinja_Dragi\\u0107evi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999925694283, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Strahinja\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strahinja_Dragi\\u0107evi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strahinja_Dragi\\u0107evi\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also defeated France 19-16 a few hours later in a game interrupted by a rain storm.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2222, \"end\": 2228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9981356933998965, \"rank\": 0.0018677487255695073, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other women's matches, Germany inflicted a first loss on Canada by 19-15 with a fine collective effort, and also beat Azerbaijan